WEBVTT

00:07:28.805 --> 00:07:32.050
The WHO cannot act
meaningfully on this issue.

00:07:32.653 --> 00:07:33.804
But the point is,

00:07:33.828 --> 00:07:37.328
a United Nations agency should
be able to act meaningfully,

00:07:37.352 --> 00:07:40.431
should be able to create binding policies
and implement them

00:07:40.455 --> 00:07:42.341
when faced with a global threat.

00:07:43.063 --> 00:07:45.498
Right now, the most we can hope for

00:07:45.522 --> 00:07:48.082
is for some world leaders
to hear our scream

00:07:48.106 --> 00:07:50.122
and decide to do the right thing.

00:07:50.146 --> 00:07:51.765
This cannot continue.

00:07:51.789 --> 00:07:53.871
In the globalized world,

00:07:53.895 --> 00:07:58.547
we need a true democratic and accountable
global system of governance.

00:07:58.571 --> 00:08:00.620
And that's also what
we're working towards,